{"title":"小芬和小桂","authors":["辛大明　沈彭年"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬和小桂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛大明　沈彭年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者按：这是一首很好的诗，原载于一九五○年三月一日出版的《大众诗歌》第一卷第三期上。作者采用了比较通俗的文字和比较生动的手法，利用五言诗的形式，叙述两个青年团员的女工参加生产突击的故事。因《大众诗歌》读者不多，我们特在五四青年节将这首诗介绍给大家。艾青同志在《人民文学》第二卷第一期《谈工人诗歌》一文中曾加以介绍，读者可以参看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双绿竹筷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整是两根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬和小桂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比这还要亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿衣穿一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃喝都不分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上工一道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下工就谈心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手艺一般好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术一样精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年团团员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想一样新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同看细纱车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活好精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是突击手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻不离分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水深总有底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高总有根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥这末亲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我讲原因："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两家住的近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来往本来亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬大一岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹来相称。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起小桂爹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车站当脚行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼子抓了走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一去没下场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说小芬爹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伪军抓壮丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一去无音信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知死与生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两家挨饥饿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纱厂去干活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块当学徒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块受折磨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常受师父骂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常挨鬼子打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里常憋气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结成大疙疸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四五年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本鬼子走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了一条狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了一条狗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋匪反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待人好狠心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累折你的筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到月不发薪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂出主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉了小芬："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他磨洋工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠心对狠心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人见亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活为自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都长精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织突击手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务要完成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己不落后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要帮别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬和小桂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争先报了名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银笛响一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗摇一摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十个突击手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个都来到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一台细纱车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全车锭子空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿纱带上线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要三分钟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都叫好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上了工人报！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击队员们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个是英豪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄缎红丝线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“突”字绣上边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击手戴上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人眼睛馋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人情绪高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要来仿效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击第二队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经组织好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二队开始搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"规矩摸不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们要一队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨人去指导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队结成团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活真叫欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨谁谁不愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急了管理员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个管理员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知甚主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂和小芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要抽一个去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说要调小芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬着了急："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是我干不好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意见可以提！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有错受批评，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也很愿意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便把我调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可不同意！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说要调小桂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂把头摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话还没出口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼把泪掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我这突击手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犯了什么罪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无故把我调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在太不对。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管理员真怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不紧也不慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道理讲起来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小桂和小芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个小‘宗派’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作需要人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为甚想不开？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年团团员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作讲价钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不为全厂好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只顾鼻子尖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二队要指导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你俩样样好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该去一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道理多明了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂和小芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要调一个去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们商量好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看谁愿意？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上一块云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二人动了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没说也没笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里想事情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬心里想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂是妹妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有事不让她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显着姐不对！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管它是那组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是突击队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都为干活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必要做对？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桂心里想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬是姐姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前帮助我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好处没法谢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去找管理员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要调就调我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去见管理员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小芬在谈话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两人对了面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都羞答答。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管理员见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旁笑哈哈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们的心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我全知道了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯转通了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疙疸解开了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹都这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全厂准搞好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争就都要争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让又全让了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有个主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知好不好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天小桂去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天轮小芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天一换人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看行不行？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俩人把头点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相把歉道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸儿红一红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相笑一笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载《大众诗歌》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}